    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Slice the <strong>aubergine<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>into thin slices then add to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Cover the dish with <strong>tin</strong> <strong>foil</strong> then cook for 15-18 min or until softened</p><p>Meanwhile, peel and slice the<strong> potatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
